Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.87,0:00:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.04,0:00:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.84,0:00:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为惩罚 命令他们两个去买零食
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.21,0:00:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说他们在这么冷的天里出去买东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.89,0:00:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 今天可是很冷的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.06,0:00:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说你看起来穿得很冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没问题的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.60,0:00:25.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古泉 好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.94,0:00:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿虚就不用关心啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.65,0:00:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来打扰啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.78,0:00:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.28,0:00:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实玖瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.78,0:00:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.04,0:00:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.99,0:00:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要调戏我家实玖瑠的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.58,0:00:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先来把我放倒了再说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.92,0:00:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要跟我决斗的意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.26,0:00:56.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不允许
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.76,0:00:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在活动室里禁止战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.93,0:01:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 社长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.06,0:01:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.56,0:01:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 实玖瑠太可爱了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.94,0:01:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那心情 我能理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.48,0:01:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能理解啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.69,0:01:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在自动贩卖机旁掉有实玖瑠的话会捡起来对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.49,0:01:16.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是猫咪比喻还是零钱比喻？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.03,0:01:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然无视我家长门就讨论可爱东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.25,0:01:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要跟他们较劲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.92,0:01:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 我接受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.38,0:01:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 接受你的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.05,0:01:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长门睡觉的时候要是对她说话的话会叫我「妈妈」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.26,0:01:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会感冒的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.26,0:01:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 再让我睡一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.10,0:01:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？这不是比喻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.18,0:01:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说那是真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.02,0:01:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.77,0:01:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实玖瑠追猫咪的话会撞到电线杆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.06,0:01:47.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仰望天空的话掉水沟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.31,0:01:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且百发百中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.48,0:01:52.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得好像我每天都会那样似的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.69,0:01:54.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说偶尔会有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.24,0:01:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 长门每天在浴室的镜子前确认肚子的状况
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.87,0:01:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.87,0:02:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.91,0:02:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是什么害羞的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.91,0:02:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你都说的这么彻底了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.00,0:02:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我要丢大招了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.96,0:02:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实玖瑠的胸前有个星形的黑痣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.04,0:02:10.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来了 我不知道的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.55,0:02:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.63,0:02:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有你的 鹤屋学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.92,0:02:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然拿出连本人都不知道的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:22.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办？这样下去的话要输了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.93,0:02:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不要煽动她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.98,0:02:29.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝仓 算了吧 你不会有奇怪的情报对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.86,0:02:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.57,0:02:32.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.86,0:02:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长门她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.99,0:02:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了即将来临的情人节偷偷的买了材料 藏起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,享受节日是好事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:54.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是喔 完全不是害羞的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.09,0:02:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有偷偷做的必要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.51,0:03:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}平安时代的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.15,0:04:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}虽说门第跟财富都很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.49,0:04:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}但不管怎么说不会和歌就不受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.12,0:04:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}因为那时是用和歌互通书信的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:52.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 阿虚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.37,0:04:54.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很痛啊 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.38,0:04:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.61,0:05:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特地出来门口来等我 真是相当用心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古泉呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.87,0:05:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,委员会那有工作 好像来不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 那正好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:33.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长门跟朝仓也好像有事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就我一人在活动室里也没事做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.50,0:05:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以今天休息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:44.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样 为了不让你非法入侵学校而在这等你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真·社长的我都没问过就擅自休息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.39,0:05:53.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非法社员的你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.77,0:05:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是13号
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才休息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.82,0:06:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.73,0:06:04.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下那边的年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.90,0:06:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 女学生 我可是很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.87,0:06:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别磨磨蹭蹭的了 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:13.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.91,0:06:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:15.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:19.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到哪去啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.54,0:06:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 虽然我想开始做了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.84,0:06:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这材料可真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.56,0:06:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都说机会是自己过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那都已经过时了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是过不过时的问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被称为不可思议的物品跟现象是不会那么容易出现
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.99,0:06:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而把他们找出来才有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:48.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.41,0:06:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以啊我们必须主动的去找 不断的发现它们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.37,0:07:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们也肯定想着被发现一直在等着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如说它们想着永远的安眠不想被打扰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去把这世界的不可思议找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.14,0:07:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪找
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.89,0:07:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:15.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:19.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道也会用不知道的方法把它找出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.98,0:07:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懂了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.15,0:07:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.99,0:07:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先是脚踏实地的做市内搜寻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你将能成为新历史的开拓者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.12,0:07:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 你想怎样就怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:42.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:47.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 我还没问呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.80,0:07:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想做怎样的巧克力？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以这些材料来看 应该是挺简单的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:08:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}长门有希的料理教室
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.89,0:08:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,融化 倒入 撒入
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.69,0:08:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就让它成型后的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:05.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是很简单的步骤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但让这孩子一个人来做的话 感觉会失败
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简单是不错啦 要不要来点复杂的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,例如❤形的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不 不用到那地步也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:21.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.92,0:08:26.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太简单的话也没有我帮忙的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.46,0:08:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 那么先把巧克力融了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.41,0:08:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.45,0:08:55.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.41,0:08:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长门 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.05,0:09:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}真正的\N朝仓凉子的料理教室
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就错了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.51,0:09:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里我们要隔水加热来融化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隔水？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不这么做的话巧克力不好融化的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.26,0:09:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 真的能融化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:26.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来需要帮忙的地方很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.58,0:09:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.67,0:09:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 这可是2月的河流啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.63,0:09:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 会感冒的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.63,0:09:52.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.51,0:09:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再找找 要找到河童为止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:56.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是白痴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.84,0:10:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别走太远了啊 摔跤了就会死的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:03.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好危险
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的没问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.87,0:10:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.87,0:10:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.91,0:10:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是有心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.66,0:10:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.00,0:10:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.17,0:10:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:44.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚 很冷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.07,0:10:54.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.57,0:10:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也知道冷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.11,0:10:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我记住喔 你这个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恨死你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.08,0:11:12.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 棒极了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.22,0:11:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:23.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿虚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.47,0:11:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得真的有河童吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.98,0:11:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道 可能真的有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,0:11:42.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日？春日！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.29,0:11:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了吧 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.00,0:11:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 区区阿虚 竟然敢先走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:57.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛！什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.92,0:11:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天要去哪里寻找呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.13,0:12:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是服了你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于做好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.31,0:12:09.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就放进冰箱让它们成型吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.93,0:12:10.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行 绝对不能熬夜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.72,0:12:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就和平常一样晚上睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:46.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回过神来已经早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.68,0:12:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈哈哈 这孩子真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.19,0:12:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧去给我洗脸！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.02,0:13:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长门 快点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.99,0:13:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:12.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长门
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.29,0:13:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.88,0:13:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 你打算什么时候把巧克力送出去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是社团活动的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.18,0:13:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.06,0:13:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须让你们2个独处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.06,0:13:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,独处？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对对 去把阿虚叫出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.40,0:13:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 困难很大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.82,0:13:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打起精神来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.36,0:13:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论怎样都是要跨过送巧克力这个障碍的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.20,0:13:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无非是稍微变难了些 别在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.16,0:13:51.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 无论变得有多困难
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都会送出去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我会送出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.01,0:14:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待已久的情人节
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.43,0:14:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.39,0:14:15.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不觉得有了什么不对吗 阿虚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:22.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷口 过甚的期待只会加深你的绝望哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:25.70,title,NTP,0,0,0,,♬今天的午饭是巧克力♬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.53,0:14:27.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不觉得有了么不对吗 阿虚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷口 放弃可以防止自己白白受伤哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长门
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.50,0:14:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早啊 要去吃饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝喵没和你在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.18,0:14:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹤屋 不要突然跑起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.43,0:14:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和朝仓约在社团活动室会合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.77,0:14:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.48,0:14:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.93,0:14:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那今天就在文艺社吃午餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实玖瑠可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我倒是没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.49,0:15:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.54,0:15:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我们教室里面里气氛很紧张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不太方便吃饭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.92,0:15:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气氛紧张？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.33,0:15:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天可是情人节啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.67,0:15:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人们的眼神都变了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹤屋 你太大惊小怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.05,0:15:35.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 这样的话如果连一点巧克力都不送
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.56,0:15:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就没办法收场啰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.23,0:15:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是实玖瑠粉丝俱乐部就有三位数了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.19,0:15:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是具体…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.73,0:15:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…应该没准备巧克力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.11,0:15:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不否定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.41,0:15:53.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个虽然是必然的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.41,0:15:58.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收巧克力的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:16:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在期待收到自己喜欢的人的巧克力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是肯定的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假装并不期待这个露骨的节日然后突然袭击什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.96,0:16:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是最好的证据吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.84,0:16:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.39,0:16:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 除此以外的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都只能算成麻烦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.27,0:16:18.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不 并不是那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.69,0:16:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹤屋！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们是人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然有喜欢 一般 讨厌 这些想法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那种事无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.53,0:16:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那不过是送出巧克力的人的自我满足嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.66,0:16:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了自己而送出去不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.91,0:16:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要介意对方的想法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着他的胸口 用力扔过去就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.09,0:16:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不能乱扔东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.01,0:16:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈哈啊哈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:56.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊真是的 忘记买饮料了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:16:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去买一下 你们先吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该很快就会回来 我们就先吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.11,0:17:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.44,0:17:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.75,0:17:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.75,0:17:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才鹤屋说的那些是在鼓励你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.05,0:17:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不是什么欺负人哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.88,0:17:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过说的稍微极端了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:44.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 要是换做是我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.06,0:17:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定会很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我要是男生的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.15,0:17:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到了长门的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的会非常开心的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.33,0:18:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么好像我在表白一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.79,0:18:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法好好表达 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.87,0:18:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 我听到了哦 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也真真切切地听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.68,0:18:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那个当成是表白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.18,0:18:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没什么问题了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实玖瑠 我有些不太说得出口的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.35,0:18:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长门的心已经完全被阿虚占领了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里好像有个很大的误会？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.77,0:18:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.82,0:18:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 要偷听？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来的路上遇到鹤屋学姐一起走到门口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现你们就像少女漫画那样互相对视着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍不住就
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就靠眼神的交流来守护着你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.96,0:18:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两个人思考回路是一样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.09,0:18:54.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像宝冢剧团一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:18:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.38,0:18:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.30,0:18:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.43,0:19:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被学姐们鼓励之后 鼓起勇气了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.68,0:19:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.18,0:19:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决站就在放学后啰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.10,0:19:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.11,0:19:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 我们就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.28,0:19:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.07,0:19:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.65,0:19:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你门
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我来讲解一下今天的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好听清楚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:30.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.13,0:19:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 长门
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把社团活动室的钥匙交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.46,0:19:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.67,0:19:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放学之后 我把这个钥匙给阿虚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.05,0:19:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并拜托他来开门
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.06,0:19:46.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在阿虚打开门的这个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.97,0:19:48.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长门过去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.52,0:19:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 多么不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.94,0:19:53.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社团活动室里面就是长门和阿虚两人的空间了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:20:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这之后 我会慢一点到活动室
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.24,0:20:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 现在就这样要怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.29,0:20:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吗 能做到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:10.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.42,0:20:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 就算不用这么故意地设计成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.63,0:20:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我尽快到活动室等他不是也可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长门 你稍微自己思考一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.68,0:20:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让阿虚在活动室里等自己过去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.76,0:20:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和自己忐忑不安的等阿虚的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.02,0:20:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底哪个比较容易做好心理准备呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.57,0:20:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 还是我过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样 就算多费一些时间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.70,0:20:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要做好心理准备 把巧克力送出去哦
